OL,3,CVeteran BBC radio presenter Steve
OL,4,CWright dies aged 69
OL,6,FSteve Wright, best known for hosting
OL,7,FBBC Radio 1 and 2, has died at the age
OL,8,Fof 69
OL,10,FSteve Wright has died at the age of
OL,11,F69, his family has announced.
OL,13,FHis family said it is "with deep
OL,14,Fsorrow and profound regret that we
OL,15,Fannounce the passing of our beloved
OL,16,FSteve Wright."
OL,18,FHe joined the in the 1970s and went on
OL,19,Fto host shows on BBC Radio 1 and 2 for
OL,20,Fmore than four decades, and was a long-
OL,21,Fstanding presenter of Top Of The Pops.
