OL,6,FThe broadcaster joined Radio 1 in 1980
OL,7,Fto host a Saturday evening show before
OL,8,Fmoving on to host Steve Wright In The
OL,9,FAfternoon a year later until 1993.
OL,11,FWright then fronted the Radio 1
OL,12,FBreakfast show for a year until 1995,
OL,13,Fand completed a stint at commercial
OL,14,Fradio stations before returning to BBC
OL,15,FRadio 2 in 1996 to host Steve Wright's
OL,16,FSaturday Show and Sunday Love Songs.
